Set Initial Global Filters in the Dashboard

If the CRM Analytics dashboard contains global filters, you can set the initial filters that are applied when the dashboard first opens. 

While editing a dashboard, select a global filter, and then click Pick Initial Values.

Choose the initial filter value for each global filter, then click Apply.

Click Done, and save the dashboard.
